All City Real Estate Ltd. Co

data.description:
Single story home sitting on over an acre with large oak trees and room for a pool! Open floor plan with beautiful stone fireplace. This large kitchen has been the source of many happy memories for the seller and is waiting for the next chef to experience all it has to offer. Spacious primary suite with coffered ceiling and twin walk-in closets. 
Large primary bathroom with double vanities, exquisite walk in shower and oversized soaking tub.  Enjoy this back covered patio and private backyard with no rear neighbors! Large 3-car tandem garage! Located in the highly acclaimed Liberty Hill ISD! Close to the new Liberty Hill public pool. Priced well under market value.
